{"tid":857648,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"(依單好笑-撻上撻) 沙頭角兩老530萬買粉嶺名都即撻 原因係...","createTime":"2018-10-11T08:38:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T10:09:06.000Z","uid":7369,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b36067d27acd5eee0e9b036b5149162dfcea7c6a","tid":857648,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T08:38:26.000Z","msg":"施政報告後，二手樓即傳來首宗撻定。<br />\n中原地產藍浩然表示，兩名屬沙頭角居民的老人家於上月28日斥530萬元購入粉嶺名都6座低層B室一個實用面積399方呎兩房單位，原計劃作自住用途，那天簽定臨時買賣合約已支付10萬元定金，並須於昨天簽定正式買賣合約。藍引述兩老表示，由於睇不好後市，樓價很不穩定，加上聲稱家人早前賣出的物業亦同被買家撻定，所以決定放棄粉嶺名都繼續交易，於施政報告後撻定離場，選擇暫時租樓，希望將來可以較平價買入。<br />\n兩老昨決定撻定，已到代理行補簽取消交易文件，並支付地產代理雙賠佣金，涉樓價2%，連同定金共損失20.6萬元。而該粉嶺名都業主殺定後，即日已把物業重新放售，叫價調低5萬至525萬元，呎價13,158元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181011/58782226\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181011%2F58782226&d=pWbpC%2BUQwT7NA%2FgVgW1ez9ZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=9fdd0118\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181011%2F58782226&h=c431d308\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181011/58782226</a>"},{"pid":"11d99f5e6db350c1cd093e9a3d223468f8d1be2f","tid":857648,"uid":39326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T08:44:26.000Z","msg":"走寶囉"},{"pid":"d271fb498f9905c534916afe07a220609b71564e","tid":857648,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11d99f5e6db350c1cd093e9a3d223468f8d1be2f","tid":857648,"uid":39326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T08:44:26.000Z","msg":"走寶囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T08:56:45.000Z","msg":"下年700萬"},{"pid":"323c7d27c4b8c8dd7932e5fe94c1261d014567eb","tid":857648,"uid":145496,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T08:59:12.000Z","msg":"廢老唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" cl